item.title: Our Journey at MACCDC
item.description: This post will cover our recent participation in the Mid-Atlantic Collegiate Cyber Defense Competition (MACCDC), where the PSU Competative Cyber Security Club’s (CCSO) elite defensive cybersecurity team made history by securing 2nd place out of 10 teams.
